{"tid":1454021,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"差婆黑心說話，重推自己仔女做搵錢工具","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:34:08.000Z","uid":38055,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf54c8aa97dfb9072b3a1529182266c1d965c7c","tid":1454021,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"(代post)<br />\n繼梅媽同Celine老母後，又再一次證明，發星媽夢嘅女人，都真係好撚變態嘅！呢個Erika仲係一個發星媽夢嘅差婆！個combo真係冇得輸！<br />\n<br />\n咩dom你想谷阿囡做明星呀？等下世啦！請大家記住呢两位姓曾，一個叫Charlotte 一個叫Kayden嘅小朋友，一見到任何品牌、傳媒有請呢两位小朋友的話，馬上响本谷舉報。然後有請各谷友去target page度落力洗版宣傳Charlotte老母的恐怖涼薄言論，講埋啲咁嘅說話仲想sell親子市場？睇吓以後會有咩品牌敢同呢個曾家嘅人合作。<br />\n<br />\n前線我唔敢上，但做鍵盤戰士出一分力我還是做得到的！陣間會接連出post，逐個品牌咁掃過去，一個不漏，請大家齊齊幫手！<br />\n<br />\n（持續更新中）<br />\n第一站: ViuTV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/654712478368002?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F654712478368002%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=f02812e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/654712478368002?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n第二站: 冷血差婆Erika Kwok老公開嘅孕婦裝公司 Mother Court<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/654720365033880?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F654720365033880%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=778b3232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/654720365033880?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n第三站: 保良局 Po Leung Kuk 林文燦英文小學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/654732278366022?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F654732278366022%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=239